name: Alphabet Profile
description:
Custom your awesome alphabet profile, available A-Z alphabet with various background color choices.


---


How to use:

  1. Choose the alphabet
  2. Choose alphabet color
  3. Choose background style
  4. Choose the color
  5. Generate :D


---


You can use to:

  1. Your project
  2. Your profile (Figma, Email, etc.)
  3. Anythings!


---


How to use to Figma profile:

  1. Generate the profile
  2. Set the frame to 2000 x 2000 px
  3. Set the border radius to 0 px
  4. Export it
  5. Set to your Figma profile :D
